[30;1m12 | [0m[35mThe biggest reason to use twine is that it securely authenticates you to PyPI[0m
[30;1m13 | [0m[35mover HTTPS using a verified connection while ``python setup.py upload`` `uses[0m
[30;1m14 | [0m[35mHTTP and exposes your credentials <http://bugs.python.org/issue12226>`_.  This[0m
[30;1m15 | [0m[35mmeans anytime you use it you expose your username and password to being[0m
[30;1m16 | [0m[35msniffed. Twine uses only verified TLS to upload to PyPI protecting your[0m
[30;1m17 | [0m[35mcredentials from theft.[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m373[0m[34m of [0m[33m837[0m[31m ]--[0m
   Rule Id: [34mBD000701[0m
       Tag: [34mSecurity.Backdoor.DataExfiltration.Token[0m
  Severity: [36mImportant[0m, Confidence: [36mHigh[0m
  Filename: [33m/twine-6.1.0/tests/fixtures/twine-1.5.0-py2.py3-none-any.whl/twine-1.5.0.dist-info/METADATA[0m
   Pattern: [32m(npm owner|password|htpasswd|auth_?token|secret_?key|private_?key|authorized_keys?|npmrc|\.ssh|usersecrets?|api_?keys|nuget\.config|\.identityservice)[0m
[30;1m43 | [0m[35mThe biggest reason to use twine is that it securely authenticates you to PyPI[0m
[30;1m44 | [0m[35mover HTTPS using a verified connection while ``python setup.py upload`` `uses[0m
[30;1m45 | [0m[35mHTTP and exposes your credentials <http://bugs.python.org/issue12226>`_.  This[0m
[30;1m46 | [0m[35mmeans anytime you use it you expose your username and password to being[0m
[30;1m47 | [0m[35msniffed. Twine uses only verified TLS to upload to PyPI protecting your[0m
[30;1m48 | [0m[35mcredentials from theft.[0m
[30;1m49 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m184 | [0m[35mKeyring Support[0m
[30;1m185 | [0m[35m---------------[0m
[30;1m186 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m187 | [0m[35mInstead of typing in your password every time you upload a distribution, Twine[0m
[30;1m188 | [0m[35mallows storing a username and password securely using `keyring`_.[0m
[30;1m189 | [0m[35mKeyring is installed with Twine but for some systems (Linux mainly) may[0m
[30;1m190 | [0m[35mrequire `additional installation steps`_.[0m
